      "fontSize": 18.45623166743253,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Nothing is stored in memory and the client needs to send the\nlast log with the reqeuest to get next batch. Client will init \nwith a default batch on load.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Nothing is stored in memory and the client needs to send the last log with the reqeuest to get next batch. Client will init with a default batch on load.",
