      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1728768657929,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "App Directory\n    -> System\n        -> network.json - WiFi / AP details (Loaded on startup)\n        -> credentials.json - Device Auth to log into the system (default is admin:admin on config)\n        -> admin.json - device details (notifications later) and general admin stored values\n    -> Logs\n        -> 1728768453.json - contains info like domain requested, ip requested, client ip etc\n        -> [more logs here]\n    -> Blacklist\n        -> example.com.json - the domain blocked, will include info like domain, nice name, category, reason",
      "fontSize": 22.462367101684013,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "App Directory\n    -> System\n        -> network.json - WiFi / AP details (Loaded on startup)\n        -> credentials.json - Device Auth to log into the system (default is admin:admin on config)\n        -> admin.json - device details (notifications later) and general admin stored values\n    -> Logs\n        -> 1728768453.json - contains info like domain requested, ip requested, client ip etc\n        -> [more logs here]\n    -> Blacklist\n        -> example.com.json - the domain blocked, will include info like domain, nice name, category, reason",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
